Author: KingZeeki
Text: My friend jokingly said loudly that I had an ed and I just got so mad and anxious.

Author: 5FootArmrest
Text: Yeah I think we can all agree that getting comments can be highly uncomfortable but soooooo satisfying if it's bc people noticed your weightloss. I crave and despise comments lol.   I just want to be thin enough to get comments and make snarky remarks lol
